  <h2>Browser support</h2>
  <p>Progress bars use CSS3 gradients, transitions, and animations to achieve all their effects. These features are not supported in Internet Explorer 7 to 9 or older versions of Firefox.</p>
  <p>Versions earlier than Internet Explorer 10 and Opera 12 do not support animations.</p>

